    {
      "parameters": {
        "chatId": "={{ $json.message.chat.id }}",
        "text": "=ü§ñ *SBS Telegram Bot Commands*\n\n*Routine Management:*\n`/complete [routine_id]` - Mark routine as complete\n`/skip [routine_id]` - Skip today's routine\n\n*System Management:*\n`/advance [system_id]` - Move system to next stage\n`/status` - View all active systems\n\n*Information:*\n`/help` - Show this help message\n\n*Quick Tip:* Use the routine_id from daily reminders to quickly complete or skip tasks!",
        "additionalFields": {
